{"tid":314373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【G20角力】白宮誤稱習近平為「中華民國總統」 台網民：故意","createTime":"2017-07-09T06:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T11:16:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1e98d52997aa8f22a6f1aa7900a15238a65ccb","tid":314373,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:55:26.000Z","msg":"【G20角力】白宮誤稱習近平為「中華民國總統」 台網民：故意<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0709 13:55&nbsp;/&nbsp;建立時間 (HKT): 0709 09:47<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普與中國國家主席習近平在G20峯會期間舉行雙邊會談，白宮事後發出特朗普的發言文本，竟誤將習近平稱為「中華民國總統」(THE REPUBLIC OF CHINA)。雖然內地媒體未有報道白宮「烏龍」事件，惟台灣一眾網民卻有超大反應。<br />\n<br />\n台灣網民直言白宮不可能犯此低級錯誤，認為事件是故意；另有網民提出白宮的錯誤，讓無數「人」心碎，甚至有人認為聲明內容仍是「一中」。　<br />\n<br />\n在大陸的社交媒體，有網民轉載，有網民稱：「丟人了！」「繙譯翻譯過來就是主席，沒毛病！」「全世界的笑料！」<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\nChan Stever：美國堅守一個中華民國<br />\n<br />\n楊容豪：還是一中啊！ok啦！<br />\n<br />\nUbon Su：白宮不可能犯這種錯誤　他們打國名已經打了幾百萬遍　顯然是故意的<br />\n<br />\nDamon Lee：有人要心碎了<br />\n<br />\nTu Sebastian：美國人心中的一個中國其實是中華民國，白宮只是不小心說了實話而已<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170709/56932466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170709%2F56932466&d=3%2Ffu82qcZ4jJTgeXT1c27LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f91338df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170709%2F56932466&h=54ab79e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170709/56932466</a>"},{"pid":"462ded20fcfdbbf479f9fdbe6ac88b83afb53731","tid":314373,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"一個中國政策下<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文<br />\nPresident of the Republic of Taiwan"},{"pid":"6eb3967f3b071def5dcd6a669620c3397a8ec798","tid":314373,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/07/09/966444-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F966444-XXL.jpg&h=83da8835&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c69333a2f53e32ef010cf57b280e95c4a9032252","tid":314373,"uid":31219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"等睇唔知邊個講錯中共做中華民國果幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6c4aaeb17ecf032a78260ad752353b53a3f029","tid":314373,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"一中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4359915a3eb11f033c3bb2be4377410d13ca6ddb","tid":314373,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"378c8d1f47cb5427f662cb1f1c8c50e0294f6840","tid":314373,"uid":65275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"射左 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8fa2125e73cbb5491d3d095b778cb239e87b8b","tid":314373,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab2a385a08f02e8334cc5035136bd7a0d098237","tid":314373,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpyBqi1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpyBqi1m.jpg&h=3ed7163c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"113dbd386cfb74ce645022e776828b6a8335b3d2","tid":314373,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpyBqi1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpyBqi1m.jp